I think I've narrowed it down. It's actually hanging on this code:
```
files = tf.concat([
  tf.train.match_filenames_once(filename)
  for filename in filenames
], axis=0)
```
If I remove the code, then the program is able to run with the data in my bucket. But I don't see anything in the source code to suggest why it's getting stuck.
